.SH DESCRIPTION

.B port-install-deps
determines the BUILD_DEPENDS, RUN_DEPENDS or all dependencies
including LIB_DEPENDS,
for the port in the current working directory using
.B make all-depends-list, make build-depends-list, or make run-depends-list,
and attempts to install all listed dependencies using pkg.
This significantly reduces the time required for a build
in the event that not all dependencies are already installed.

.SH RETURN VALUES

0 on success, non-zero error codes otherwise

